version_description: I transcribed the chords from the official sheet music of this song. Especially the chords in the chorus and the outro should be more accurate than any version I found in here.

Thouroughly ear-transcribed / well-aligned and complete chords for all parts of the song / reading using capo 4th fret (play F, sounds A) / suggestions for playable voicings / tab for changes in intro and verse.
From "A Monster Calls" Original Motion Picture Soundtrack.
Added some other ways to play some chords that sound very nice.

song_name: To The End Of The Earth
